{"tid":729420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國獨立日(7月4日)","createTime":"2018-07-04T14:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:52:35.000Z","uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d50f39eff9f7a57bc09755f25507a431accce4bc","tid":729420,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"美國革命期間，1776年7月2日第二屆大陸會議表決通過維珍尼亞州的理察&middot;亨利&middot;李提出的一項宣示獨立決定的提案時，十三個殖民地已在法理上脫離英國。[4][5]在投票通過獨立後，大陸會議開始關注《美國獨立宣言》的制定，此宣言解釋了獨立的緣由。獨立宣言由五人委員會準備，主要作者為托馬斯&middot;傑斐遜。其後大陸會議對文本內容進行了修改和辯論，最終在7月4日得以通過。"},{"pid":"3b6ac6bb7cf36a6bb74ab8abcfbf952618849da7","tid":729420,"uid":146728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58982cdbb7e3273d44ebddadbfc83b1ee4431ee9","tid":729420,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd1574e1b8652a2216e582d8a83db22d4dd515a","tid":729420,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}